cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem.knapsack
Class KnapsackIterator

java.lang.Object
  cz.cvut.felk.cig.jcop.problem.knapsack.KnapsackIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
OperationIterator, java.util.Iterator<Operation>
public class KnapsackIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements OperationIterator

Iterator over knapsack operations.

For every knapsack item, iterator returns either AddOperation or RemoveOperation, depending if item is in configuration present or not. Items with lower index are parsed prior to items with higher index.

getRandomOperation

public Operation getRandomOperation()
                             throws java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException
Description copied from interface: OperationIterator
Returns randomly chosen operation.

Note that internal counter is not changed, therefore subsequent calls to next will be unaffected by getRandomOperation.

Also, two calls of getRandomOperation could possibly return the same operation.
